1.0.name: wordpress/wp-boxes
1.0.description: WP Boxes is a box based clean theme for WordPress that gives your blog a classy and professional look. 4 Extra Widgetized area for better customization and monetization. Author Box, Opengraph, Page Navigation and also social sharing buttons are integrated with the theme.
